# Rainforest Journey Pack
<!--text-->
Who wouldn’t dream of a kit that contains everything to guarantee you a superb fishing adventure in the wild rainforest? The powerful Aguarayo™ 6' 7 (200) SE spinning rod for distance casts of heavy lures. Selva Star 7500 SE reel with a large spool to land strong and swift South American predators. Special lures for the Amazon fish: weighted walkers, hunched runners, top softbaits, new swimbaits… But the big ticket item is your Pond Pass to Maku-Maku Lake and a Advanced Fishing License for the exotic Peru!

Rainforest Journey Pack includes:
* 40000 CREDITS
* 20 BAITCOINS
* 7-DAY PREMIUM
* 25 Storage Slots
* 1 Tackle Setup Slot
* 5 Marker Buoys

RODS ‘N REELS
Rods:
* MagFin™ Aguarayo™ 6' 7" (200) SE - Length: 6' 7" (2.0 m); Lure Weight: 1 3/4 – 2 5/6 Oz (50–80 g); Power: X-Heavy; Line Weight: 37.4–72.7 lb (17–33 kg); Action: Mod Fast
Reels:
* MagFin™ Selva Star 7500 SE - Ratio: 5.5; Recovery: 34.5" (88 cm); Capacity: Mono 37/128 (0.6/128), Braid 36/230 (0.3/230); Max Drag: 70.5 Lb (32 kg); Drag: Front

TERMINAL TACKLE
Lines - Length: 1000 yd (1000 m)
* Braid .013" (0.32 mm) - Test: 69.5 Lb (31.5 kg)
* Fluoro .032" (0.8 mm) - Test: 70.5 Lb (32 kg)
Leaders:
* Titanium Leader .016" (0.4) (x10) - Length: 0.82’ (0.25 m); Test: 69.6 Lb (31.6 kg)
* Titanium Leader .016" (0.4) (x10) - Length: 1.64’ (0.5 m); Test: 69.6 Lb (31.6 kg)
* Fluorocarbon Leader .030" (0.8) (x10) - Length: 0.82’ (0.25 m); Test: 70.5 Lb (32.0 kg)
* Fluorocarbon Leader .030" (0.8) (x10) - Length: 1.64’ (0.5 m); Test: 70.5 Lb (32.0 kg)
Lures:
* Jig Heads: JigHead 2 Oz. (56 g), #4/0 (x5), JigHead 2 Oz. (56 g), #6/0 (x5), JigHead 2 1/4 Oz. (64 g), #4/0 (x5), JigHead 2 1/4 Oz. (64 g), #6/0 (x5)
* Topwater Lures: Walker 2 Oz. (56 g), #4/0 (x2)
* Minnows: Hunched Runner 26 ft (8m), #5/0 (x2)
* Swimbaits: Swimbait 2 1/4 Oz. (64 g), #4/0 (x3), Swimbait 2 1/2 Oz. (71 g), #5/0 (x2)
Soft Baits:
* Craws: Nymphes 4" (10 cm) (x20)
* Slugs: Slug 4" (10 cm) (x20)
* Grubs: Twin Tail Spider Grub 4" (10 cm) (x20)

EQUIPMENT
* Garry Scott™ FishCitadel L Plus Keepnet  - Max Single Fish Weight: 220 Lb (100 kg); Total Fish Weight: 551 Lb (250 kg)

POND PASSES (7 days):
MAKU-MAKU LAKE

FISHING LICENSES (7 days):
Advanced Peru License
